Package org.linuxforhealth.fhir.cql.engine.converter.impl

Class FHIRTypeConverterImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.linuxforhealth.fhir.cql.engine.converter.impl.FHIRTypeConverterImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FHIRTypeConverter
    public class FHIRTypeConverterImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements FHIRTypeConverter
    This is a default implementation of the FHIRTypeConverter interface that converts IBM FHIR Server model objects to and from CQL types.
